QuestData.Title: Something Stewed
QuestData.Description: Finally, we're going to need a feast. And none of that "finger food" stuff! This crowd wants meat, and lots of it.$B$BGather up venison from Highland elk and does. Highland worg are good eatin' too - bring back some ribs. We'll show you a feast like you've never had in all the Eastern Kingdoms, friend.
QuestData.LogDescription: Gather 8 slabs of Fresh Venison and 5 Worg Ribs.
QuestData.RewardText: Lookat that! You're practically bent double under the weight of all that meat. I'd better get my people cooking.
